email:
Celebrate Monument Valley's momentous return with Monument Valley: The Trilogy 

For the first time ever, experience the complete, award-winning Monument Valley series in one physical collection.
Quiet, calming, and totally engrossing, the Monument Valley trilogy stands as one of the great triumphs of modern indie gaming. Each title in ustwo games’ beloved puzzle series tells an intimate, meditative story through the power of gorgeous visuals and spellbinding gameplay. 

Monument Valley is especially important to us here at iam8bit. You can’t chronicle our journey without mentioning the partnership with ustwo games in those earlier days, creating vinyl records, plushies, and even socks for their seminal platform puzzler. 

That’s why it’s our great honor to bring you this collection today. For the first time ever, all three Monument Valley titles have been brought together on physical media, with all the love and care they deserve. This is the Monument Valley: The Trilogy Exclusive Edition. 

Monument Valley 1, Monument Valley 2, and Monument Valley 3 are presented here, complete in all their splendor. Plus, we’re including an exclusive o-sleeve, only available on iam8bit.com. And to celebrate the rich visuals that made Monument Valley so legendary, we’re also including six art cards featuring scenes from the games. 
 
To top it off, when you pre-order now, you'll receive a digital download code for all 3 award-winning soundtracks.

Whether you’re returning to these games or stepping into their breathtaking world for the first time, this collection is the definitive way to experience everything Monument Valley has to offer.
